   DEBUG: 2026-03-09 18:03:28,414:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: TEAMMATES
   DEBUG: 2026-03-09 18:03:28,415:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: ]
   DEBUG: 2026-03-09 18:03:28,416:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: , we
